### =========================
### 🚗 GET ALL CARS
### =========================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cars


### =========================
### ➕ ADD NEW CAR
### =========================
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "BMW M4 Competition",
  "price": 120,
  "type": "Sports",
  "image": "https://example.com/bmw.jpg",
  "seats": 4,
  "description": "Luxury sports car"
}


### =========================
### ✏️ UPDATE CAR
### =========================
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/cars/PUT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 150,
  "description": "Updated car description"
}


### =========================
### 🗑 DELETE CAR
### =========================
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/cars/PUT_ID_HERE